data.description: **POSSIBLE 2.55% LOAN ASSUMPTION! - must qualify**  Nestled at the rear of the subdivision, this 5348 SF Italian style luxury home offers an amazing view of the Boise foothills & Bogus Basin. Built by J Bar K on a spacious .50 acre lot, it features 5 beds, 4 baths, and an expansive 3-car garage. Boasting a premier location amidst Eagle's finest homes, the property emphasizes both views and privacy in its stunning backyard. The entertainer's dream floorplan showcases a gourmet kitchen with WOLF Stainless Cooktop/Double Oven, Subzero fridge, granite countertops, and a grand center island. With a primary suite and 2nd Junior suite on the main level, formal and informal dining, ornate tile floors, & a theatre room, this meticulously crafted home is adorned with detailed Alder woodwork and Anderson wood windows. The East-facing backyard, complete with a covered patio, firepit, and a heated pool with a hot-tub & slide, adds the perfect finishing touch to this exquisite residence. Welcome home to luxury living.
